@startuml Cashier Flow
title Cashier Process Flow

actor Cashier
participant System

== Login ==
Cashier -> System: Enter Credentials
activate System
System -> System: Authenticate
System --> Cashier: Grant Access
deactivate System

== View Orders ==
Cashier -> System: Access Order List
activate System
System -> System: Fetch All Orders
System --> Cashier: Display Orders (with filters)
deactivate System

== Process Customer Order ==
Cashier -> System: Create New Order
activate System
System -> System: Validate Stock
alt Stock Available
    System -> System: Create Order
    System -> System: Reserve Stock
    System -> System: Log Transaction
    System --> Cashier: Order Created Successfully
else Stock Unavailable
    System --> Cashier: Show Error - Insufficient Stock
end
deactivate System

== Record Payment ==
Cashier -> System: Record Customer Payment
activate System
System -> System: Validate Payment
System -> System: Create Transaction Record
System -> System: Update Transaction Log
System --> Cashier: Payment Recorded
deactivate System

== View Personal Dashboard ==
Cashier -> System: Access Personal Dashboard
activate System
System -> System: Calculate Today's Total
System -> System: Aggregate Transactions
System -> System: Breakdown by Type
System --> Cashier: Display Dashboard (Today's Stats)
deactivate System

== View Daily Report ==
Cashier -> System: Request Daily Report
activate System
System -> System: Select Report Date
System -> System: Fetch Delivered Orders
System -> System: Calculate Income
System -> System: Breakdown by Product
System --> Cashier: Display Daily Report
deactivate System

== View Monthly Report ==
Cashier -> System: Request Monthly Report
activate System
System -> System: Select Month/Year
System -> System: Fetch Month Orders
System -> System: Calculate Monthly Income
System -> System: Daily Breakdown
System -> System: Product Breakdown
System --> Cashier: Display Monthly Report
deactivate System

@enduml
